---
title: Pan-Seared Chicken & Creamy Dill Sauce with Mashed Potato & Garlic Veggies
description: We’ve paired succulent chicken with a creamy dill sauce to keep things super simple tonight. With a delicious mash and crisp veggies as the perfect sidekicks, you’ve got a classic meal that’s easy to love.
